          <text><![CDATA[<p>SNAP Transparency Act of 2013 - Amends the Food and Nutrition Act of 2008 to direct the Secretary of Agriculture (USDA) to: (1) establish a uniform reporting system to enable retail stores participating in the supplemental nutrition assistance program (SNAP, formerly the food stamp program) to collect and provide the Secretary with detailed information on SNAP-purchased food items, and (2) publish such information on the Internet.</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <updateDate>2013-04-25T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
